name: Recollection of a Meal - CRISS CROSS POTATOES
description: Historical Log of Apocalyptic Events Near You is proud to enchant your visual senses with: A marvelous collaboration of The Noble Tuber and the Blood of Olives! Allow this offering to seep it's oily pleasure directly into your retina! Dip your memories in the sauce, and get lost in it's starchy embrace!
